{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/post-data-with-the-javascript-xmlhttprequest-method","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"json-apis-and-ajax","demoType":null,"title":"Pošalji podatke putem JavaScript XMLHttpRequest-a","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U prethodnim primerima, primili ste podatke sa eksternog resursa. Takođe možete poslati podatke na eksternom resursu, pod uslovom da taj resurs podržava AJAX zahteve i znate URL.</p>\n<p>Putanja za JavaScript na <code>XMLHttpRequest</code> takođe se koristi za slanje podataka na server. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\nxhr.open('POST', url, true);\r\nxhr.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json; charset=UTF-8');\r\nxhr.onreadystatechange = function () {\r\n  if (xhr.readyState === 4 &#x26;&#x26; xhr.status === 201) {\r\n    const serverResponse = JSON.parse(xhr.response);\r\n    document.getElementsByClassName('message')[0].textContent =\r\n      serverResponse.userName + serverResponse.suffix;\r\n  }\r\n};\r\nconst body = JSON.stringify({ userName: userName, suffix: ' loves cats!' });\r\nxhr.send(body);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Vi ste već videli neke od ovih metoda. Ovde metoda <code>open</code> inicijalizuje zahtev kao <code>POST</code> za dostupan eksterni resurs URL, i prosleđuje <code>true</code> kao treći parametar - što ukazuje da se ta operacija izvršava asinhrono.</p>\n<p>Metoda <code>setRequestHeader</code> postavlja vrednost zaglavlja zahteva za HTTP, koje sadrži informacije o pošiljaocu i zahtevu. Mora se pozvati nakon metode <code>open</code>, ali pre metode <code>send</code>. Dva parametra su ime zaglavlja i vrednost za postavljanje kao telo tog zaglavlja.</p>\n<p>Sledeći, handler događaja za <code>onreadystatechange</code> obrađuje promene statusa zahteva. <code>readyState</code> od <code>4</code> znači da je operacija završena, a <code>status</code> od <code>201</code> znači da je zahtev uspešan. Stoga, HTML dokumenta se može ažurirati.</p>\n<p>Konačno, putanja <code>send</code> šalje zahtev sa vrednošću <code>body</code>. <code>body</code> uključuje <code>userName</code> i funkciju <code>suffix</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7faf367417b2b2512be9","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ispravite kod da napravite zahtev za <code>POST</code> koristeći krajnju tačku (endpoint) API. Zatim unesite svoje ime u polje za unos i kliknite na <code>Send Message</code>. Vaša AJAX funkcija bi trebalo da promeni <code>Reply from Server will be here.</code> sa podacima sa servera. Formatirajte odgovor da prikažete vaše ime uz tekst od <code> loves cats</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"data-visualization","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301504,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/post-data-with-the-javascript-xmlhttprequest-method"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\r\n    document.getElementById('sendMessage').onclick = function () {\r\n      const userName = document.getElementById('name').value;\r\n      const url = 'https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts';\r\n      // Add your code below this line\r\n\r\n      // Add your code above this line\r\n    };\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  body {\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;\r\n  }\r\n  h1 {\r\n    font-size: 2em;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n  .box {\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    background-color: #eee;\r\n    padding: 20px 5px;\r\n  }\r\n  button {\r\n    color: white;\r\n    background-color: #4791d0;\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #4791d0;\r\n    padding: 5px 10px 8px 10px;\r\n  }\r\n  button:hover {\r\n    background-color: #0f5897;\r\n    border: 1px solid #0f5897;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<h1>Cat Friends</h1>\r\n<p class=\"message box\">Reply from Server will be here</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  <label for=\"name\"\r\n    >Your name:\r\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" />\r\n  </label>\r\n  <button id=\"sendMessage\">Send Message</button>\r\n</p>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da kreira <code>XMLHttpRequest</code> novi.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /new\\s*XMLHttpRequest\\(\\s*\\)/g);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>open</code> za iniciranje zahteva <code>POST</code> na serveru.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /\\.open\\(\\s*('|\")POST\\1\\s*,\\s*url\\s*,\\s*true\\s*\\)/g);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>setRequestHeader</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /\\.setRequestHeader\\(\\s*('|\")Content-Type\\1\\s*,\\s*('|\")application\\/json;\\s*charset=UTF-8\\2\\s*\\)/g\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da ima hendlera događaja za <code>onreadystatechange</code>, postavljenog u metodu.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /\\.onreadystatechange\\s*=/g);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod bi trebalo da dohvati element sa klasom <code>message</code> i promeni njegovu <code>textContent</code> u <code>userName loves cats</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /document\\.getElementsByClassName\\(\\s*('|\")message\\1\\s*\\)\\[0\\]\\.textContent\\s*=\\s*.+?\\.userName\\s*\\+\\s*.+?\\.suffix/g\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da koristi <code>send</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /\\.send\\(\\s*body\\s*\\)/g);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/data-visualization/#json-apis-and-ajax","dashedName":"post-data-with-the-javascript-xmlhttprequest-method","certification":"data-visualization","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"data-visualization","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"json-apis-and-ajax","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/data-visualization/data-visualization-projects/visualize-data-with-a-bar-chart","prevChallengePath":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/get-geolocation-data-to-find-a-users-gps-coordinates","id":"587d7faf367417b2b2512be9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":6,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<script>\r\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\r\n    document.getElementById('sendMessage').onclick = function () {\r\n      const userName = document.getElementById('name').value;\r\n      const url = 'https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts';\r\n      // Add your code below this line\r\n      const xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\n      xhr.open('POST', url, true);\r\n      xhr.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json; charset=UTF-8');\r\n      xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {\r\n        if (xhr.readyState === 4 && xhr.status === 201) {\r\n          const serverResponse = JSON.parse(xhr.response);\r\n          document.getElementsByClassName('message')[0].textContent =\r\n            serverResponse.userName + serverResponse.suffix;\r\n        }\r\n      };\r\n      const body = JSON.stringify({\r\n        userName: userName,\r\n        suffix: ' loves cats!'\r\n      });\r\n      xhr.send(body);\r\n      // Add your code above this line\r\n    };\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  body {\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;\r\n  }\r\n  h1 {\r\n    font-size: 2em;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n  .box {\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    background-color: #eee;\r\n    padding: 20px 5px;\r\n  }\r\n  button {\r\n    color: white;\r\n    background-color: #4791d0;\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #4791d0;\r\n    padding: 5px 10px 8px 10px;\r\n  }\r\n  button:hover {\r\n    background-color: #0f5897;\r\n    border: 1px solid #0f5897;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<h1>Cat Friends</h1>\r\n<p class=\"message\">Reply from Server will be here</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  <label for=\"name\"\r\n    >Your name:\r\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" />\r\n  </label>\r\n  <button id=\"sendMessage\">Send Message</button>\r\n</p>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/post-data-with-the-javascript-xmlhttprequest-method"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}